title: RBS profit overshadowed by DOJ impasse
text:
RBS profit overshadowed by DOJ impasse 1:28pm GMT - 01:38 
Royal Bank of Scotland reports its first full-year profit in a decade, but Friday's milestone is bitter-sweet for the British bank which had hoped to get a multi billion-dollar misconduct charge out of the way in 2017. Kate King reports.
